Data was obtained from https://www.kaggle.com/uciml/breast-cancer-wisconsin-data/version/2#data.csv in April 2020.


Data included 
	* radius
	* texture
	* perimeter
	* compactness 
	* symmetry 
of suspicious breast tissue


Different Classification Models were used:
	* Logistic Regression
	* Decision Tree
	* Random Forest Classifier
	* SVC


Analysis focused on 
	* Confusion Matrix
	* ROC
	* AUC
	* Recall
